Khamel - Something like a HAML parser in PHP

For the moment, see the example usage at the bottom of khamel.php.

Khamel indents using single spaces. If you want it to default to double spaces, modify Khamel::spaces() to double its parameter. The root element’s direct children (usually <head>, <body>) won’t get indented, because the root element’s output indent is -1. The static variable Khamel::$root_indent controls this feature.
